---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/CertificationCard.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Certifications"
	description="A comprehensive list of certifications for Why AI LLC, showcasing expertise in Deep Learning, Generative AI, MLOps, and more."
>
    <h1>Certifications & Specialized Skills</h1>
    <p>My commitment to continuous learning is demonstrated by a deep and broad range of certifications. Below are some highlights, with a focus on my specializations in Deep Learning and Distributed Computing.</p>

    <h2>Deep Learning & Neural Networks</h2>
    <p>This collection of certifications represents a deep dive into the theory and application of deep learning, from foundational concepts to advanced, state-of-the-art architectures.</p>
    <div class="cert-grid">
        <Card provider="TensorFlow" title="TensorFlow Developer Certificate" />
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="Deep Learning Specialization" />
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="TensorFlow: Advanced Techniques Specialization" />
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="Convolutional Neural Networks" />
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="Sequence Models" />
        <Card provider="Coursera" title="Generative Deep Learning with TensorFlow" />
        <Card provider="Coursera" title="Advanced Computer Vision with TensorFlow" />
        <Card provider="DataCamp" title="Deep Learning with PyTorch" />
    </div>

    <h2>Generative AI & Language Models</h2>
    <p>A deep dive into the world of Large Language Models, from application development to advanced retrieval and fine-tuning.</p>
    <div class="cert-grid">
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="LangChain for LLM Application Development" />
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="Finetuning Large Language Models" />
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="Advanced Retrieval for AI with Chroma" />
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="Knowledge Graphs for RAG" />
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="Understanding and Applying Text Embeddings" />
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="Getting Structured LLM Output" />
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="Embedding Models: From Architecture to Implementation" />
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="LLMs as Operating Systems: Agent Memory" />
    </div>

    <h2>LLMOps, MLOps, & Distributed Computing</h2>
    <p>These certifications showcase my expertise in operationalizing machine learning models at scale, with a focus on robust, production-grade systems and distributed computation.</p>
    <div class="cert-grid">
        <Card provider="Google" title="GCP Professional ML Engineer" date="Pending" />
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="LLMOps" />
        <Card provider="DeepLearning AI" title="Automated Testing for LLMOps" />
        <Card provider="Coursera" title="Machine Learning Engineering for Production (MLOps) Specialization" />
        <Card provider="Coursera" title="ML Pipelines on Google Cloud" />
        <Card provider="DataCamp" title="Parallel Computing with Dask" />
    </div>

    <h2>Foundational Machine Learning & Time Series Analysis</h2>
    <p>A selection of my other certifications, with a special focus on Time Series analysis, which has been a cornerstone of my career.</p>
    <div class="cert-grid">
